  <section id="retention">
    <h2>6. Data retention</h2>
    <p>
      We keep signup emails for as long as you wish to receive Conan updates, or
      until you unsubscribe or ask us to remove you. Purchase records are
      retained as required for tax and accounting purposes.
    </p>
